cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with person re-identification using convolutional neural networks and attention mechanisms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning and optimization, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves large-scale evaluations, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of attention mechanisms and feature representations could also suggest cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as possible categories.
